 grnmtn = Hike.create(user_id: admin.id, title: 'Green Mountain Loop via Chautaqua Trail', city: 'Boulder', state: 'Colorado', difficulty: 5, length: 6, pet_friendly: true, directions: 'In Boulder, travel west on Baseline from Broadway. After about 1 mile, turn south on Kinnikinic Rd and park at trailhead. This is a busy place in summer, you might have to park on Baseline Rd.', extra_info: 'A popular peak hike providing views of the Indian Peaks and Boulder that features beautiful wild flowers in the spring and summer. ')
