 dlt = Hike.create(user_id: admin.id, title: 'Sand Dunes Loop Trail', city: 'Mosca', state: 'Colorado', difficulty: 3, length: 5, pet_friendly: true, directions: 'From Mosca take CO-17 North then turn right onto Lane 6 N for 12 miles. Then turn left onto CO-150 N and take that for about 3 miles.', extra_info: 'Medano Creek is one of the rare creeks in the world where a system of rhythmic waves is created from surging seasonal waters over a smooth creek bed with a steep gradient to give it enough speed. The waters are highest in May and June, but usually almost nonexistent by the Visitor Center by the fall. Snow can still be present in the park into May.')
